{
  "stem": "9899.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want to take them with me because it is cold, the winter will come, and I have nothing for them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So the German said, OK, but I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll go with you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I will go with you because if you go alone, they will not let you in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the officer went with my mother into the house, and he says to her, in the meantime, your house, because it's on the hill, has become the [? center ?] of operations for the Germans, so we have taken over your house.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we have not touched your clothes, so you will go in and take everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As they were approaching the house, and my mother was going to go in and look in the back to see if all was well, a German comes out, a soldier.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he asks, who is this woman?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the officer says, she has lived here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is her house, and she's come to pick up the clothes for her children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She'll just be in and out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So he says, or is she coming looking for the Jew we found here in the backyard yesterday?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So my mother, that was the end of her courage, that was the end of her wisdom.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of-- of-- she was so distraught, she couldn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So the German-- the officer says, look what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The woman has not been here for two days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "What happened in her absence, it is not-- none of her concern.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She came here with me for her things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Let her get in, get her things, and I'll take her back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So God was watching over us after all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In a way, he was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He took the-- he told my mother to go in.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
